Program Details:
This system is a Java-based Payroll System that reads employee data and attendance records from files. 

The user logs in as either Employee or Payroll Staff.

Employee can: Enter Employee Number to view salary details

Payroll Staff can: Process payroll for one employee, Process payroll for all employees

The system computes:
Total hours worked
Gross salary
Deductions (SSS, PhilHealth, Pag-IBIG, Tax)
Net salary

All data is read using FileReader and BufferedReader.

